@LeadFraudDetection.Api_HostAddress = http://localhost:5282
@token = YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### Login as Admin
POST {{LeadFraudDetection.Api_HostAddress}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@example.com",
  "password": "Admin123!"
}

### Login as User
POST {{LeadFraudDetection.Api_HostAddress}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "user@example.com",
  "password": "User123!"
}

### Get All Leads (requires authentication)
GET {{LeadFraudDetection.Api_HostAddress}}/api/leads
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Lead by ID
GET {{LeadFraudDetection.Api_HostAddress}}/api/leads/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Create New Lead (triggers fraud detection)
POST {{LeadFraudDetection.Api_HostAddress}}/api/leads
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "phoneNumber": "1234567890",
  "ipAddress": "192.168.1.1",
  "userAgent": "Mozilla/5.0",
  "firstName": "John",
  "lastName": "Doe",
  "company": "Test Company"
}

### Create Lead with Disposable Email
POST {{LeadFraudDetection.Api_HostAddress}}/api/leads
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "fraud@tempmail.com",
  "phoneNumber": "9999999999",
  "ipAddress": "10.0.0.1",
  "userAgent": "",
  "firstName": "Suspicious",
  "lastName": "User",
  "company": ""
}

### Check Fraud for Existing Lead
POST {{LeadFraudDetection.Api_HostAddress}}/api/leads/1/check-fraud
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get All Blacklist Entries (Admin only)
GET {{LeadFraudDetection.Api_HostAddress}}/api/blacklist
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Check if Email is Blacklisted
GET {{LeadFraudDetection.Api_HostAddress}}/api/blacklist/check?type=Email&value=fraud@example.com
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Add Email to Blacklist (Admin only)
POST {{LeadFraudDetection.Api_HostAddress}}/api/blacklist
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "type": "Email",
  "value": "fraud@example.com",
  "reason": "Known fraudster",
  "isActive": true
}

### Add IP to Blacklist (Admin only)
POST {{LeadFraudDetection.Api_HostAddress}}/api/blacklist
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "type": "IP",
  "value": "192.0.2.1",
  "reason": "Suspicious activity",
  "isActive": true
}

### Remove Blacklist Entry (Admin only)
DELETE {{LeadFraudDetection.Api_HostAddress}}/api/blacklist/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###
